Charles E. Fowler et al., appellees, v. Hi-Lo Fan Corporation et al., defendants, on appeal of Victor H. Leinweber et al., appellants.Gen. No. 35,635.Henry G. Hardy, for appellants. Louis P. Miller, for appellees. Mr. Presiding Justice Gridley delivered the opinion of the court.

Opinion filed May 17, 1932.

Rehearing denied May 31, 1932.
